casebody.data:
No. 10-7240. Larry Billian, Petitioner v. United States. 562 U.S. 1059, 131 S. Ct. 686,

178 L. Ed. 2d 475,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 9383. November 29, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied. Petitioner is allowed until December 20, 2010, within which to pay the docketing fee required by Rule 38(a) and to submit a petition in compliance with Rule 33.1 of the Rules of this Court.

Same case below, 383 Fed. Appx. 538.
